chapters.title: Intro
n Palestine a might prophet of God
This prophecy must be fulfilled
Matt. 13:24
Vernon Wayne Howell
Mt. Carmel Center
Matthew 17:1-4 (KJV)
The two witness in Revelation 11:2
Elijah the same person?
They were bold and fearless in preaching, even before kings.
1 the message will be bold and fearless even before kings
Elijah #3 (Mark 13:9) Ye shall be brought before rulers and kings for my sake, for a testimony against them.
They had a simple diet and lifestyle. Elijah #1 (1 Kings 17:11)
They dressed in modest, simple clothing. Elijah # 1-( 2 kings 1:8)
Elijah #3 ...modesty in dress and, simple clothing Ephesians 4:24 "Put on the new man, which after God is created in righteousness and true holiness."
They believed in discipling others.
They preached a baptism of repentance and death to self. Elijah- #1 (2 kings 2:6)
They preached a baptism of repentance and death to self. Elijah- #2 ( Matthew 3:5-6).
They were both baptized with the supplication (prayer) Elijah- # 2 ( Luke 11:1)
It will call men and women, boy and girl to develop a PEAYER LIFE. Elijah- #3 Acts 9: 11
They both endured religious persecution.
The message will bring on religious persecution. Elijah- #3 (Revelation 12:17)
They both repaired the altar of God.
It will restore TRUE WORSHIP- (The Altar)
Their messages sparked revival and reformation.
